column2: ALPHA BLACK TO BRAVO BLACK. WE ARE IN THE LZ. ITS SAFE. COME TO PICK US UP. OVER.
ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. THREE SCUD LAUNCHERS HAVE BEEN NEUTRALIZED. OVER.
BRAVO TO ALPHA. GET READY FOR EXTRACTION. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA BLACK. EXCELLENT WORK. NOW HEAD TO THE EXTRACT LZ. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA BLACK. WELCOME TO HOME. I HOPE YOU HAD SUCCESSFUL HUNT. OVER.
Scud Hunt day 3, in the forest behind enemy lines
